<title>jmʿnạ sẖwq</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 (jmʿnạ sẖwq wạḥd ạ̹lyk .. nsẖwf jmạlk yạ mlyk)2
 [(ạlms bṭyfk qlbnạ)2 .. ạlʿṭsẖạn wshrạn bynạdyk]2
 (bnsbḥ ạlạ̹sm ạljmyl .. whtạfnạ lyk ṭwl ạlsbyl)2
 [(wạ̹n mr lyl ạ̉w ṭạl ẓlạm)2 .. nwrk ynwr kl lyl]2
 (ạsẖtqnạ llfrḥẗ mʿạk .. ạsẖtqnạ nthny̱ brḍạk)2
 (zyl ạlgẖywm wạmḥi ạlhmwm)2 .. nrfʿ jnạḥạtnạ fy smạk
 (ậh mwlạy ḥbk .. ybhj ạlqlb ạlkỷyb
 ậh mwlạy ʿṭfk .. rạḥẗ ạldạr llgẖryb)2
 [(zyl ạlgẖywm wạmḥi ạlhmwm)2 .. nrfʿ jnạḥạtnạ fy smạk]2</lyrics>
